HEADWORD: Coehorn
<hw>Coe"horn</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From its inventor,
Baron <etsep>Coehorn</etsep>.]</ety> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>A small
